---
title: Preply

pageClassName: p-home
---
extends shared/_layout-main

block modal
	mixin modalContent1()
		.c-modal__header
			p What kind of tutors does Preply look for?
		.c-modal__body
			p No specific certification or teaching experience is required! We welcome English tutors who:
			ul
				li
					span Enjoy sharing knowledge and making a difference to students’ lives
				li
					span Have outstanding communication skills
				li
					span Are willing to provide a personalized learning experience to international students

	+modal('ques1', 'modalContent1')
	mixin modalContent2()
		.c-modal__header
			p How do you become a tutor?
		.c-modal__body
			p It’s easy to start and easy to earn! Sign up and create a tutor profile. We’ll check it within 5 business days.
			p Once your profile is approved, students from around the world will see it on Preply and will be able to book lessons with you. Also, you’ll have access to useful tools, training webinars and teaching materials for your lessons.
			p!= "Learn more about creating a tutor profile. [<a href='#'>https://help.preply.com/en/articles/4175138-register-as-a-tutor</a>]"

	+modal('ques2', 'modalContent2')
	mixin modalContent3()
		.c-modal__header
			p What does Preply offer?
		.c-modal__body
			ul
				li
					span An opportunity to earn by sharing what you know
				li
					span A steady stream of new students looking for English tutors
				li
					span Convenient tools for managing your lessons and connecting with students
				li
					span Safe payment methods (Paypal, Payoneer or Skrill)
				li
					span Learning plans and tests to save you time on lesson preparation
				li
					span Support from our friendly team through training webinars, live chat and email

	+modal('ques3', 'modalContent3')
	mixin modalContent4()
		.c-modal__header
			p Are there any additional requirements?
		.c-modal__body
			p You will need a stable internet connection, a webcam, and a microphone for conducting lessons in the virtual classroom. And, of course, a passion for teaching English to help your students reach their goals!

	+modal('ques4', 'modalContent4')
	mixin modalContent5()
		.c-modal__header
			p Is it free to display a tutor profile on Preply?
		.c-modal__body
			p Yes. It is free to create a tutor profile, get exposure to students, and use Preply’s tools and materials.
			p We only charge a commission when a tutor starts to get bookings from students. The more hours you teach on Preply, the lower the rate of commission.
			p!= "Learn more about how Preply tutors get paid. <a href='#'>https://preply.com/en/help/model</a>"

	+modal('ques5', 'modalContent5')

block content
	div.body.body--start(class!= pageClassName)

		include components/main/_main
		include components/main/_benefits
		include components/main/_teach
		include components/main/_reviews
		include components/main/_ques
		include components/main/_paid
